    "id": "R63_14",
    "content": "**PRIMARY: Unit Tests** (`python run_tests.py`)\n- **Purpose**: Fast feedback during development (478 tests in ~6 seconds)\n- **Scope**: Individual component testing with dependency injection\n- **Isolation**: Mock implementations from `tests/fixtures/mock_implementations.py`\n- **No External Dependencies**: No I/O, APIs, or file system operations\n- **Coverage**: Test all business logic, error handling, and edge cases",
    "project": "petermodzelewski_yt-database",
    "file": "structure.md",
    "first_level": "Quality Assurance",
    "second_level": "Testing Strategy"
  },
  {
    "id": "R63_15",
    "content": "**SECONDARY: Integration Tests** (`python -m pytest tests/integration/`)\n- **Purpose**: End-to-end validation before releases (13 tests in ~90 seconds)\n- **Scope**: Real external APIs with `.env-test` configuration\n- **Environment**: Test database \"YT Summaries [TEST]\" for safe testing\n- **Coverage**: Full pipeline testing with actual YouTube and Notion APIs",
    "project": "petermodzelewski_yt-database",
    "file": "structure.md",
    "first_level": "Quality Assurance",
    "second_level": "Testing Strategy"
